      "title": "Changement climatique : Causes et controverses",
      "summary": "Analyse du consensus scientifique sur le réchauffement climatique et des arguments climato-sceptiques",
      "posture": "neutre_critique",
      "tags": ["tag_climat", "tag_science", "tag_environnement", "tag_politique"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "claims": [
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440101",
      "text": "Le changement climatique est principalement causé par les activités humaines",
      "stance": "pro",
      "strength": "high",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440102",
      "text": "Le climat a toujours changé naturellement, l'influence humaine est surestimée",
      "stance": "con",
      "strength": "weak",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440103",
      "text": "97% des climatologues s'accordent sur le réchauffement d'origine anthropique",
      "stance": "pro",
      "strength": "high",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440104",
      "text": "Le consensus scientifique est biaisé par des intérêts financiers et politiques",
      "stance": "con",
      "strength": "weak",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440105",
      "text": "Les modèles climatiques prédisent avec précision les tendances observées",
      "stance": "pro",
      "strength": "high",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440106",
      "text": "Les modèles climatiques sont trop imprécis pour être fiables",
      "stance": "con",
      "strength": "weak",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440107",
      "text": "Les événements extrêmes (canicules, inondations) augmentent en fréquence et en intensité",
      "stance": "pro",
      "strength": "high",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440108",
      "text": "Les médias exagèrent les événements météorologiques pour créer de la peur",
      "stance": "con",
      "strength": "weak",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440109",
      "text": "La transition énergétique est techniquement et économiquement viable",
      "stance": "pro",
      "strength": "medium",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440110",
      "text": "La transition énergétique coûtera trop cher et détruira l'économie",
      "stance": "con",
      "strength": "medium",
      "topics": ["d50e8400-e29b-41d4-a716-446655440001"],
      "createdAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-01-15T18:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
